00:35:47,520 --> 00:35:48,520
<i>Tu consegues!</i>

443
00:35:51,200 --> 00:35:52,200
Olá.

444
00:35:54,400 --> 00:35:57,880
- Olá. Corri até à outra praia.
- Certo.

445
00:35:57,960 --> 00:36:03,920
